snippet: Will Power kept Penske Racing perfect this year at 3-0, picking his way through the field in Long Beach, Calif., to win his second consecutive IndyCar Series race.
abstract: Will Power wins his second consecutive IndyCar Series race in Long Beach, Calif; other auto racing results noted.
lead_paragraph: Will Power kept Penske Racing perfect this year at 3-0, picking his way through the field in Long Beach, Calif., to win his second consecutive IndyCar Series race.

headline.main: Power Keeps Penske IndyCar Team Unbeaten
